
Users REST API
* Retrieve all users
    GET/users

* Create new User
    POST/users

* Retrieve one User
    GET/users/{id}

* Delete a user
    DELETE/users/{id}


*Posts REST API
    *Retrieve all posts for a user
        GET/users/{id}/posts

    * Create a post for a user
        POST/users/{id}/posts

    * Retrieve details of a post
        GET/users/{id}/posts/{post_id}


Details-
User: id, name, birthdate
Post: id, description


